OL,3,CThe future of the Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrikes rests on ACAS but who are they?
OL,6,FIt comes as talks to resolve the
OL,7,FBirmingham bin strikes now rest on
OL,8,FAcas as a deal between Unite the union
OL,9,Fand Birmingham City Council could be
OL,10,Fwithin "touching distance".
OL,12,FThat was according to Unite, who
OL,13,Frepresent bin workers.
OL,15,FThe union and the council have resumed
OL,16,Ftalks for a third time. Strikes
OL,17,Fbetween bin workers employed by the
OL,18,Fcouncil and Unite the union are in
OL,19,Ftheir seventh week.
