OL,3,CThe future of the Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrikes rests on ACAS but who are they?
OL,6,FKevin Rowan, Acas director of dispute
OL,7,Fresolution, said: "We can confirm that
OL,8,FBirmingham City Council and Unite have
OL,9,Fagreed to Acas conciliation talks to
OL,10,Fhelp them resolve the current dispute
OL,11,Finvolving refuse workers.
OL,13,F"The talks are scheduled to take place
OL,14,Fon 1 May."
OL,16,FAcas is an independent public body
OL,17,Fthat receives funding from the
OL,18,Fgovernment.
