OL,3,CThe future of the Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrikes rests on ACAS but who are they?
OL,6,FDue to a number of bin workers and
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council trying to find
OL,8,Fa resolution, the talks next week will
OL,9,Ffall under Acas' "collective
OL,10,Fconciliation" approach.
OL,12,FThis will be done by a neutral person
OL,13,F(an Acas conciliator), Acas told us
OL,14,Fthey bring an "impartial, fresh
OL,15,Fperspective that can help to break the
OL,16,Fdeadlock, finding the common ground
OL,17,Fthat will help parties find a way
OL,18,Fforward".
