OL,3,CThe future of the Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrikes rests on ACAS but who are they?
OL,6,FAcas say collective conciliation is
OL,7,Fflexible. Where a conciliator will
OL,8,Fnormally begin by having informal
OL,9,Fdiscussions with both sides, either
OL,10,Fjointly or separately, to understand
OL,11,Fthe issues in the dispute.
OL,13,FThey'll encourage both sides to
OL,14,Fconsider their options for finding a
OL,15,Fsolution. Acas helps by creating a
OL,16,Fpositive environment to have
OL,17,Fdiscussions.
