OL,3,CThe future of the Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrikes rests on ACAS but who are they?
OL,6,FIf both sides agree a solution, the
OL,7,Fconciliator can help them draft a
OL,8,Fwritten agreement. The conciliator's
OL,9,Frole is to then make sure that
OL,10,Feveryone understands what has been
OL,11,Fagreed.
OL,13,FAcas says between 2023-24 they handled
OL,14,Fmore than 600 Collective Conciliation
OL,15,Fcases, reaching a settlement in 94% of
OL,16,Fthose - next week will reveal whether
OL,17,Fthe Birmingham bin strikes will be the
OL,18,Fnext dispute to be resolved or not.
