OL,3,CThe future of the Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrikes rests on ACAS but who are they?
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Frecently said: "We could be in
OL,8,Ftouching distance of a deal but
OL,9,FBirmingham City Council is again
OL,10,Fguilty of saying one thing in public
OL,11,Fand another in the negotiations..
OL,13,F"This flip flopping needs to be sorted
OL,14,Fprior to the Acas negotiations next
OL,15,Fweek, so the dispute can be resolved
OL,16,Fand end the uncertainty for workers
OL,17,Fand the misery for Birmingham
OL,18,Fresidents."
